*gen_grbl.machineDescription: Use this if you have a GRBL machine

settings.gcodeStart:
G21         ; Set units to mm
G90         ; Absolute positioning
M4 S0       ; Enable Laser/Spindle (0 power)

*gen_smoothie.machineDescription: Use this if you have a SMOOTHIE machine

settings.gcodeStart:
G21         ; Set units to mm
G90         ; Absolute positioning

*emblaser2.machineDescription: Use this if you have an Emblaser 2 from Darkly Labs

*FabKit.machineDescription: Use this if you have an FabKit from FabCreator

settings.gcodeStart:
G21         ; Set units to mm
G90         ; Absolute positioning
M3           ; Laser On
M106       ; Compressor On
settings.gcodeEnd:
M5                       ;Laser off
G28.2XY              ; Home X & Y
M107                   ;Compressor Off
